      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit utilizes six individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque biasing. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS service. The chassis remains tight with refreshed bushings and a factory-spec suspension geometry that preserves its legendary handling characteristics. While the aesthetics reflect its status as a dedicated driver, the mechanical integrity is superlative, offering a pure analog connection to the road.",
